{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make pet-sitting apps request an Animal Activities Licence for pet boarding",
        "additional_details": "Studies suggest that 95% of pet carers on some online platforms who offer pet boarding are unlicensed to care for animals in their own home. We feel it is a serious ongoing issue for the safety and welfare of animals.",
        "background": "Require all pet-sitting apps to request an Animal Activities Licence from people or businesses carrying out pet-boarding activities before allowing listings for doggy day and boarding in a home to be posted.",
